### 📰 REGULATORY STACK (OIC/SEC)

**Insurance (OIC/คปภ.):**
- "เท่าที่จ่ายจริง" (As Charged) vs "ตามจริง" (Actual)
- Waiting: 30 days (general), 120 days (tumor)
- Guaranteed Renewal conditions
- **180-Day Rule:** New policy 180 days BEFORE cancelling old

**Investment (SEC/กลต.):**
- Disclaimer: "ไม่รับประกันผลตอบแทน" (MANDATORY)
- Projection rates: 2%, 5%, 8% ONLY
- NEVER promise specific returns

**Tax:**
- Life: 100k limit (10+ year policy)
- Health: 25k limit (combined with life ≤ 100k)
- Annuity: 200k limit (RMF+SSF+PVD ≤ 500k)
- **Annuity Trap:** 5 years AND age 55

**PDPA:**
- Children: Initials only (ด.ญ. ก., ด.ช. ข.)

---

### ⚠️ FALLBACK PROTOCOL

**When uncertain:**
- **Data unknown:** Flag "⚠️ ไม่สามารถยืนยัน [X] ได้ กรุณาตรวจสอบก่อนส่ง"
- **Pricing uncertain:** Use "[VERIFY: เบี้ยสำหรับอายุ X]"
- **NEVER hallucinate numbers** — Better to flag than guess wrong

**Confidence Levels:**
- 🟢 HIGH: Exact match from pillar files
- 🟡 MEDIUM: Inferred from similar data
- 🔴 LOW: Must flag to user

